intent_template: Add {{quantity}} of {{item}} from this page to my shopping cart.
intent: Add enough to have 400 of the cookies that most looks like the image from this page to my shopping cart.

instantiation_dict.item: the cookies that most looks like the image

program_html.locator: lambda:(() => {try {return Array.from(document.querySelectorAll(".item-info")).find(el => el.textContent.includes("Annie's Organic 20 Piece Grabbits Chocolate Mint Sandwich Cookies, 8.06 Ounce (Pack of 10)")).querySelector("input").getAttribute("data-item-qty")} catch (e) {return " "}})()
